status.description:
The status of the goods receipt. There are the following possible statuses: 
1) CANCELLATION_FAILED_TO_POST_TO_TARGET_SYS: Cancellation has been triggered for the goods receipt, yet the cancellation to the integrated ERP system failed; 
2) CANCELLATION_POSTED_IN_DMC: Cancellation has been triggered for the goods receipt, and it has been successfully posted in SAP Digital Manufacturing; 
3) CANCELLATION_POSTED_TO_TARGET_SYS: Cancellation has been triggered for the goods receipt, and it has been successfully posted in both SAP Digital Manufacturing and the integrated ERP system; 
4) FAILED_TO_POST_TO_TARGET_SYS: Goods receipt posting to the integrated ERP system failed; 
5) POSTED_IN_DMC: Goods receipt has been successfully posted in SAP Digital Manufacturing; 
6) POSTED_TO_TARGET_SYS: Goods receipt has been successfully posted in both SAP Digital Manufacturing and the integrated ERP system.
